// EditorToolbar
// Toolbar rendered above the editor area. Contains item name, zoom controls,
// undo/redo, history dropdown, overflow menu for export/format/copy actions,
// and an optional history diff banner.

FUNCTION handleToggleOverflow() -> void
  Toggles the overflow menu open/closed.

---

FUNCTION handleActionClick(action) -> void
  Calls action.onClick(). Closes overflow menu.

---

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(ts) -> string
  Used for the history diff banner timestamp.
  Just now (<5s), Xs ago (<60s), Xm ago (<1h), Xh ago (<24h),
  Yesterday, Xd ago, or locale date string.

---

FUNCTION EditorToolbar(item, ...) -> JSX                               EXPORT
  CALLS: HistoryDiffSettingsDropdown (HistoryDiffSettingsDropdown),
         DesignHistoryDropdown (DesignHistoryDropdown),
         DiagramHistoryDropdown (DiagramHistoryDropdown)
  Builds allActions array: overflow actions + export SVG/PNG + format
  (diagrams) + copy (snippets) + add comment/approve all/reject all/clear
  proposals (annotation actions).
  Renders:
    - Optional history diff banner (with HistoryDiffSettingsDropdown) when
      historyDiff is active.
    - Main toolbar row containing:
        document -> HistoryToolbar
        diagram/design -> undo/redo buttons + history dropdown
        item name + unsaved indicator dot
        inlineControls slot (caller-injected buttons)
        zoom controls (out, level, in, center, fit) for non-snippet/non-document
        rotate button (diagrams only)
        overflow menu button + popover
